title: #92Noon! Gleeman/StumpSnob/Hasan/Birk/Carter
description: Opening with fodder from Aaron Gleeman, followed by Stump the Snob with Cory Cove and Saucer...The Athletic's Arif Hasan with football opinions leads into the Birk Bit midway thru the show...Ryan Carter begins the final stretch to reminisce about a Wild Classic game, with football talkers to close the show!
